    public class SQLiteHouseKeeper.DefaultSignals
extends SQLiteHouseSignalAPI
    A default implementation of SQLiteHouseSignalAPI for this keeper class. The "domain" string is defaulted to the canonical name of the SQLiteHouse implementation to which the keeper is bound.
